{"data":[{"date":"14:44 11/07","title":"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/dan-sao-real-tri-an-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Ramos, Bale v\u00e0 Asensio b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m ph\u1ee5c khi chia tay ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\"Nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u1eefng con s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f9ng nhau \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Anh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 CLB n\u00e0y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean t\u00ean anh. Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea1nh anh. M\u1ed9t c\u00e1i \u00f4m n\u1ed3ng th\u1eafm v\u00e0 ch\u00fac may m\u1eafn\", Sergio Ramos vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram ngay sau khi Real \u0111\u0103ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chia tay Ronaldo.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u00e0n sao Real tri \u00e2n Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Untitled-7110-1531267573.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ramos t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 ch\u00fac Ronaldo may m\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau khi c\u00f3 tin anh ra \u0111i. \u1ea2nh: Mail Online.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italy chi 126 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 33 tu\u1ed5i. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Serie A k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Ronaldo s\u1ebd gi\u00fap v\u1ef1c d\u1eady gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eebng m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u00e0 t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ronaldo, vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Instagram: \"M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u1eadt vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea1nh anh trong 5 n\u0103m qua. Ch\u00fac may m\u1eafn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u00e9 b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Marco Asensio cho r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo l\u00e0 h\u00ecnh m\u1eabu cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 anh. Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u00e0y t\u1ecf: \"Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh anh. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh. T\u00f4i ch\u00fac anh may m\u1eafn trong b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 ghi 450 b\u00e0n sau 438 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, gi\u00e0nh b\u1ed1n Cup v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League v\u00e0 b\u1ed1n danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga sau 9 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4136","checkdouble":"190947"},{"date":"13:38 11/07","title":"N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-4 U20 N\u1eef Australia (KT): Thua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e0nh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3 khu v\u1ef1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-16h00-ngay-117.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e3 thua to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Australia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018. Tuy\u1ebft Dung l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM 2-4 U20 N\u1eee AUSTRALIA\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Highlight-Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 1<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tuy\u1ec3n n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1eb7c trang ph\u1ee5c truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 5: Hai \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u01b0u th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n h\u01a1i nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 U20 n\u1eef Australia v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT TH\u1ee8 8: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 U20 Australia v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh th\u00ec N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi b\u00e0n thua\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-08.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 17: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM M\u1ede T\u1ef6 S\u1ed0. D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha ra ch\u00e2n hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Tuy\u1ebft Dung, n\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-16.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 18: U20 N\u1eee AUSTRALIA MAU CH\u00d3NG G\u1ee0 H\u00d2A. Tuy v\u1eady, l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng 1 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-18.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 23: U20 N\u1eef Australia v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1ed3n \u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ra s\u1ee9c v\u00e2y h\u00e3m c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n Kim Thanh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 26: U20 N\u1eef Australia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00e1 xa nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eb3ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng ch\u00fat n\u1eefa bay tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-26.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 27: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u00fat xa t\u1eeb ph\u00eda U20 N\u1eef Australia v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng bay ch\u1ec7ch m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong gang t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 29: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 hay v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ph\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba U20 n\u1eef Australia. S\u1ed1 23 Ho\u00e0ng Qu\u1ef3nh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u1ebft th\u00fac cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng song th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee9u thua.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-29.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 35: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM B\u1eca D\u1eaaN 1-2. S\u1ed1 21 c\u1ee7a U20 N\u1eef Australia, Nevin tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t xa nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng bay c\u1ef1c hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0o g\u00f3c cao v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-35.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 42: Sau khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c tri\u1ec3n khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 s\u1eafc b\u00e9n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Hi\u1ec7p 1 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-2 d\u00e0nh cho U20 N\u1eef Australia. N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Tuy\u1ebft Dung nh\u01b0ng do s\u1ef1 thua k\u00e9m v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHI\u1ec6P 2<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u0103ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng s\u1edbm ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn song n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u00ec nguy c\u01a1 thua th\u00eam l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 52: QU\u00c1 \u0110\u00c1NG TI\u1ebeC. N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a nh\u01b0ng s\u1ed1 12 H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U20 N\u1eef Australia trong pha \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-52.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 60: N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e2m v\u00e0o b\u1ebf t\u1eafc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi th\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 64: M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U20 N\u1eef Australia \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00f3m g\u1ecdn.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-63.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 65: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM NH\u1eacN B\u00c0N THUA TH\u1ee8 3. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Cross c\u1ee7a U20 N\u1eef Australia c\u00f3 pha x\u1eed l\u00fd \u1edf g\u00f3c h\u1eb9p, gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n h\u01a1n l\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh bay s\u00e2u n\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-65.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 69: C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I. H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n khi tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U20 N\u1eef Australia song c\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 74: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u00e0nh cho n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam, l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-74.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 76: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM NH\u1eacN B\u00c0N THUA TH\u1ee8 4. Chidiac, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u1ea1ch 16m50. B\u00f3ng \u0111i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kim Thanh ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9u thua.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-76.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 79: QU\u00c1 \u0110\u00c1NG TI\u1ebeC. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U20 n\u1eef Australia \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh lao ra kh\u1ecfi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m nh\u1eb1m ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb H\u1ea3i Y\u1ebfn v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua. Tuy v\u1eady, s\u1ed1 12 c\u1ee7a n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i x\u1eed l\u00fd qu\u00e1 v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng tr\u00fang c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf tr\u1ed1ng.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-79.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 85: Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 an b\u00e0i v\u00e0 gi\u1edd N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 song m\u1ecdi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 \u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- PH\u00daT 87: M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam tung ra c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb s\u00e1t v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng bay qua x\u00e0 ngang.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-87.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- PH\u00daT 90: N\u1eee VI\u1ec6T NAM GHI TH\u00caM B\u00c0N DANH D\u1ef0. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 11m th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ed1 7 Tuy\u1ebft Dung.\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/11/Nu-Viet-Nam-vs-U20-Nu-Australia-90.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n- Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n th\u1eafng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 U20 N\u1eef Australia.\u00a0R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng d\u00f9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i song v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c1, Australia kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110TQG n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft. C\u00f2n th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV\u00a0Mai \u0110\u1ee9c Chung \u0111\u00e0nh tranh h\u1ea1ng 3.<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4135","checkdouble":"190944"},{"date":"15:21 11/07","title":"CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t sau v\u1ee5 n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/clb-nam-dinh-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-sau-vu-nao-loan-tren-san-thien-truong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a VFF trong chi\u1ec1u 11/7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh sau v\u1ee5 C\u0110V tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n h\u00e0nh hung tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League.</h2><h2>CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a VFF</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Nam Dinh\" title=\"C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/clb-nam-dinh-chinh-thuc-nhan-an-phat-sau-vu-nao-loan-tren-san-thien-truong.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 do \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng v\u00f2ng 18 V-League di\u1ec5n ra cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, cay c\u00fa sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 thi\u00ean v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch SLNA, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e9m nhi\u1ec1u v\u1eadt l\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u0103ng m\u1ea1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n, bu\u1ed9c BTC s\u00e2n v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an ninh ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eb9p y\u00ean t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, BTC s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an ninh, an to\u00e0n cho t\u1ed5 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Nam.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Thi\u00ean Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh 50 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 20 c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018 (tr\u1eadn Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh vs Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 21/7 t\u1edbi). \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec3m trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u01a1n TP.HCM 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2019 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4134","checkdouble":"190948"},{"date":"12:09 11/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: V\u00ec b\u1ecb M.U ph\u1ee5 b\u1ea1c, Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111i theo \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m\u201d Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u00f4ng tin Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a CR7 m\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Man United, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e0nh cho anh nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u00e0n th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Perez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1eeb c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y, th\u00f4ng tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</span> \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Italia g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi Real Madrid b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m \u1edf c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Real, Florentino Perez &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4 h\u01a1n. R\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Juventus s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 mua Ronaldo l\u00ean con s\u1ed1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, &ldquo;B\u1ed1 gi\u00e0&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Bongda24h v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/goc-nhin-cristiano-ronaldo-gia-nhap-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Cristiano Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, vi\u1ec7c Perez &ldquo;l\u00e0m gi\u00e1&rdquo; v\u1edbi Juventus l\u1ea1i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho Ronaldo. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Juve d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u. Theo c\u00e1ch ngh\u0129 n\u00e0y, Perez gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra th\u1eed th\u00e1ch cho nh\u00e0 trai tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1ea3 con g\u00e1i \u0111i (c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u1ea5m l\u00f2ng l\u1eabn ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&rdquo; r\u1eddi Real</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus theo h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 4 n\u0103m. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n CR7 \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 r\u1eddi Real v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do. G\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, n\u01a1i anh ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh: &ldquo;\u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi gian t\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f9ng Real Madrid&rdquo; s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00ec qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u01a1n (kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n di\u1ec5n ra trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" title=\"Ronaldo muon chia tay Real tu lau\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Ronaldo-muon-chia-tay-Real-tu-lau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CR7 t\u1eebng nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, sau nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan thu\u1ebf T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1ea5t m\u00e3n v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real. L\u00fd do anh \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ed1i ren.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay t\u1eeb l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, th\u00f4ng tin Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Anh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jorge Mendes c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Manchester United v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Paris Saint Germain \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng PSG nhanh ch\u00f3ng r\u00fat lui b\u1edfi c\u00f2n m\u1ea3i m\u00ea Neymar v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo va Mourinho\" title=\"Ronaldo va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Ronaldo-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo b\u1ecb c\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t b\u1edfi M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00e1i nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 M.U, n\u01a1i t\u1eebng c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jose Mourinho, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi anh. M\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gareth Bale t\u1edbi M.U nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn gi\u1eefa hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i \u1edf Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec v\u1eady, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e0nh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Real. Nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ebft Lionel Messi v\u00e0 Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona v\u00e0 PSG d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfn CR7 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi suy ngh\u0129. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd s\u1edbm t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cho Ronaldo t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p song \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2017/18 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.&nbsp; <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n chia ch\u00e1c khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Real Madrid n\u0103m 2009, nh\u01b0ng MU v\u1eabn thu v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n sau khi Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thua k\u00e9m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai trong l\u00e0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1eabn thu nh\u1eadp. Anh c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi t\u1eeb M\u1ef9, Trung \u0110\u00f4ng hay Trung Qu\u1ed1c..., nh\u1eefng n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p k\u00e9m. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00e1t khao gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Ronaldo nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Anh, Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Italia. V\u00e0 sau c\u00f9ng, Juventus \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng v\u00f2ng tay ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n anh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea3m m\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSang Juventus, Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 b\u1ecb c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 FIAT s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y d\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 l\u1edbn cho Ronaldo. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong kho\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u1ed7i n\u0103m m\u00e0 anh l\u0129nh t\u1ea1i Juve, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u cho h\u00e3ng xe c\u00f3 tr\u1ee5 s\u1edf t\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CDV Juventus chao mung Ronaldo\" title=\"CDV Juventus chao mung Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/CDV-Juventus-chao-mung-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n c\u1ee7a C\u0110V&nbsp;Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Juventus v\u1eabn c\u00f2n k\u00e9m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb so v\u1edbi Messi ho\u1eb7c Neymar, song nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn 9 tri\u1ec7u Euro/ n\u0103m so v\u1edbi khi c\u00f2n \u1edf Real. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf r\u1eb1ng Juve th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khao kh\u00e1t s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ronaldo. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u0129 kh\u00e1c: ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 22 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a r\u00f5 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Juventus s\u1ebd ra sao. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m c\u1ee7a CLB m\u1edbi d\u00e0nh cho m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea1t t\u1edbi t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi ch\u00f3p bu Real. Juventus lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1eb7t CLB l\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ebft d\u00f9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Ronaldo b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo dat duoc thoa thuan toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/CHINH-THUC-Cristiano-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CR7 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/cristiano-ronaldo-gui-tam-thu-day-xuc-dong-toi-real-madrid-180-190889.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7y x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Real</span>, chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a anh d\u00e0nh cho CLB v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ed1t 9 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. G\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 n\u0103m, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec n\u00f3i l\u1eddi t\u1eeb bi\u1ec7t. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n cho anh. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Real hay M.U, l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, &ldquo;B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0&rdquo; Juventus m\u1edbi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1 v\u1edbi CR7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/david-trezeguet-noi-gi-ve-thuong-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-190885.html\">David Trezeguet n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo-184-190838.html\">T\u00e2n binh Juventus h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo-421-190836.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ea3i Ly (TTVN)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4133","checkdouble":"190940"},{"date":"15:14 11/07","title":"Real Madrid quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/real-madrid-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo AS, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf l\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus</span> v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng: &ldquo;Real x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00fang c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Gareth-Bale-roi-Real-khong-the-xay-ra-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Real mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Real, Ronaldo s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCR7 s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Serie A anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a. C\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Higuain \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 g\u1eedi Real Madrid, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf t\u00ecnh y\u00eau r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real gi\u1eef Bale \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo AS, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Gareth Bale r\u1eddi Real kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/real-madrid-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-gareth-bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Bale mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real sau khi gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1 2018 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo ra \u0111i, Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 tha thi\u1ebft gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales \u1edf l\u1ea1i. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp g\u1eb7p Bale \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bale s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n cho th\u1ea5y t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi Real kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n CR7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n MU, Tottenham v\u00e0 Bayern Munich l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Bale, song v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4132","checkdouble":"190943"},{"date":"16:03 11/07","title":"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Everton mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Goal, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Pique v\u00e0 Umtiti, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton mua Yerry Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Everton mua Yerry Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/everton-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-hang-thai-barca-voi-gia-24-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Barcelona</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Mina trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong 3 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00fap Colombia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng 1/8. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u1ea3 kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina-180-190671.html\" target=\"_blank\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mina</span>, bao g\u1ed3m Tottenham, Everton v\u00e0 M.U. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Everton ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Mina</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton mua Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo Goal, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina ghi ban mo ti so.\" title=\"Yerry Mina ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Yerry Mina\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ba Nha \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Barca nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf cao 1m95 c\u1ee7a Mina l\u00e0 v\u0169 kh\u00ed l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a\u00a0Everton \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Barca, h\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed do ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4131","checkdouble":"190953"},{"date":"16:59 11/07","title":"Infographics: Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid - Ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/infographics-cristiano-ronaldo-chia-tay-real-madrid-ra-di-de-lai-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y, huy hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Santiago Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ng n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real Madrid n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh Madrid n\u00f3i chung qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Infographics Cristiano Ronaldo chia tay Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/Infographics-Cristiano-Ronaldo-chia-tay-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i b\u00e2y gi\u1edd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng bi\u1ebft \u01a1n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1eed t\u1ebf v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf ra, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do v\u00ec sao t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 mong mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00edn n\u0103m di\u1ec7u k\u1ef3 t\u1ea1i n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00edn n\u0103m th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Ch\u00edn n\u0103m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi, nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00ec nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd th\u1ea5p. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vui ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 trao cho t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo2\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163634-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo3\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163644-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nT\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u hay chia s\u1ebb ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m n\u1ed3ng \u1ea5m t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng nhau, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ba ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap b\u1ea1c b\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n trong n\u0103m n\u0103m. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1n Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 ba danh hi\u1ec7u Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i th\u1eadt qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed7i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo4\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo5\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163701-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea th\u1eddi gian ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo6\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo6\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163712-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo7\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo7\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163722-7.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Khu v\u1ef1c ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nV\u00e0 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m tr\u1ecdn trong tim t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i. H\u01a1n l\u00fac n\u00e0o h\u1ebft, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t th\u1ea3y m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi: xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch, ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9, tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec3n khai tr\u01a1n tru \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eebng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo8\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo8\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163734-8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9c ghi b\u00e0n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo9\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163744-9.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo10\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo10\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/163753-10.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo11\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo11\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/11.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i, ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i hay b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u?</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo12\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo12\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Infographics: Loi tam biet cua Cristiano Ronaldo13\" title=\"Infographics: L\u1eddi t\u1ea1m bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo13\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/11/13.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Qua ch\u00edn n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1. T\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u00e2u, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n gi\u1eef m\u1ed9t l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y, huy hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Santiago Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 t\u00f4i xin g\u1eedi l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u n\u00f3i m\u00e0 ch\u00edn n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng h\u00e9t l\u00ean: Hala Madrid!&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">-Cristiano Ronaldo- <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em><strong>(D\u1ecbch: Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng GP)<br>\r\nInfographics by Marca (Vi\u1ec7t h\u00f3a b\u1edfi Bongda24h.vn)</strong></em></div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4130","checkdouble":"190961"},{"date":"14:58 11/07","title":"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-juventus-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, Mediaset Premium kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Rugani\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i thay c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus trong th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-mua-Daniele-Rugani-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c David Luiz \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i c\u00f2n Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i bu\u1ed9c Sarri ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua trung v\u1ec7 Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Empoli, c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRugani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng, song m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus. Ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u0169 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-hoan-thanh-2-ban-hop-dong-vao-dau-thang-7-172-189593.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Daniele Rugani </span>th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, Mediaset Premium kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh The Blues \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rugani nhieu kha nang se tro thanh tan binh dau tien cua Arsenal o He 2018\" title=\"Rugani nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-juventus-voi-gia-35-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rugani \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn t\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, Juventus cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Sarri ra m\u1eaft Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mediaset Premium, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Chelsea, t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge anh s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. The Blues \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4129","checkdouble":"190942"},{"date":"15:41 11/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 PSG chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Kante?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, PSG thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Thiago Motta \u0111\u00e3 36 tu\u1ed5i, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1982 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ee5 PSG mua Kante v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/6/thuc-hu-vu-psg-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m NGolo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/psg-chi-so-tien-sieu-khung-mua-sao-chelsea-172-188620.html\" target=\"_blank\">PSG quan t\u00e2m Kante</span> c\u1ee7a Chelsea, HLV Thomas Tuchel \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed The Sun c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 Kante b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n n\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m d\u1ebbo dai.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKante c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng minh trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a PSG s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn PSG ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Kante</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mua Kante ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante duoc cham diem cao nhat tran Leicester vs Chelsea\" title=\"Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cao nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Leicester vs Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/19/Real,-Barca-va-PSG-muon-dua-tien-ve-Kante-roi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho Kante\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o d\u00e0nh cho Kante, v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kante l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1eafp thay Antonio Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues gi\u1eef Kante \u1edf l\u1ea1i. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh y\u00eau v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Kante r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4128","checkdouble":"190952"},{"date":"17:15 11/07","title":"Lucas Torreira \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u khi so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/lucas-torreira-o-dau-khi-so-sanh-voi-nhung-tien-ve-phong-ngu-hang-dau-ngoai-hang-anh.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. C\u00f9ng so s\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Sampdoria, Lucas Torreira c\u00f3 31 l\u1ea7n ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 0.88 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal N\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/Lucas-Torreira-toi-Arsenal-Nang-cap-chat-thep-noi-tuyen-giua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira (s\u1ed1 14) c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Kante (26, 0.78 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Henderson (20, 0.83 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Matic (56, 1.62 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Fernandinho (65, 2.03 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Eric Dier (82, 2.61 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn).</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Arsenal th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 72 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 2.03 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn. V\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Henderson (31, 1.28 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Fernandinho (47, 1.47 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn), Dier (48, 1.53 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Matic (64, 1.85 l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m duy nh\u1ea5t Kante (85, 2.55&nbsp;l\u1ea7n/tr\u1eadn).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1eb7n b\u00f3ng, Torreira th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 57 l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi trung b\u00ecnh 1.61 l\u1ea7n, h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Henderson ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 40, Fernandinho l\u00e0 41, Dier v\u00e0 Kante c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 43 c\u00f2n Matic l\u00e0 56.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:</strong> Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Torreira l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Lucas Torreira t\u1edbi Arsenal</span> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ed1t c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u1ee9ng c\u00e1p h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Torreira th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n trung b\u00ecnh 61.83 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 87%. V\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n/90 ph\u00fat, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Kante (65), Dier (65), Matic (75), Henderson (86) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (93).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira tao ra kha nhieu cho cac dong doi\" title=\"Torreira t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/chuyen.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, con s\u1ed1 87% c\u1ee7a Torreira t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n Henderson (84%) v\u00e0 Dier (86%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i k\u00e9m h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Matic (88%), Kante (89%) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (90%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 t\u1ea1o ra 36 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, trung b\u00ecnh 1.02 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i/90 ph\u00fat. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Dier (15), Fernandinho (21), Matic (24) v\u00e0 Henderson (25) nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Kante (41).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Torreira l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80%, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Henderson (53%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Kante, Matic (c\u00f9ng 83%), Dier (87%) v\u00e0 Fernandinho (88%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn: </strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Torreira kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, song s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00e0 anh t\u1ea1o ra l\u1ea1i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Torreira c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 2.85 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 68%. Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi Matic (59%), Fernandinho (60%), Henderson (60%), Kante (66%) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ea1nh Eric Dier (70%).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Torreira co loi choi rat ran\" title=\"Torreira c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t r\u1eafn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/11/ran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Torreira c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t r\u1eafn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Arsenal ch\u1ec9 cao 1m68, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 k\u00e9m, v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 39%, t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n duy nh\u1ea5t Kante (35%) v\u00e0 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Fernandinho (55%), Dier (57%), Matic (67%) v\u00e0 Henderson (72%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111eo b\u00e1m dai d\u1eb3ng, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trung b\u00ecnh anh ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi 2.35 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat, cao h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Fernandinho (0.84), Matic (0.65), Henderson (0.58), Kante (0.45) v\u00e0 Dier (0.25).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:</strong> Torreira r\u1ea5t ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng, t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a Arsenal l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4127","checkdouble":"190962"},{"date":"17:46 11/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU s\u0103n sao s\u00e1ng Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/thuc-hu-vu-mu-san-rebic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic cho bi\u1ebft Eintract Frankfurt ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho Ante Rebic nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.</h2><h2>Rebic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Eintract Frankfurt theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Fiorentina tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u1ee9t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Rebic \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m t\u0103ng g\u1ea5p nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Croatia v\u00f9i d\u1eadp Argentina 3-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 Rebic ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u1edf Premier League ch\u00fa \u00fd n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng Man United, Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i Rebic. Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Bayern Munich c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<h2>Rebic ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/thuc-hu-vu-mu-san-rebic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>MU ch\u01b0a g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rebic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic c\u00f2n 3 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Frankfurt nh\u01b0ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Ante Rebic c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Croatia. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u theo d\u00f5i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup c\u00f9ng nhau \u1edf tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi th\u1ea5y Rebic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn cho Rebic. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 Rebic \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Eintract Frankfurt kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU kh\u00e1c:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-kiem-duoc-bao-nhieu-tu-thuong-vu-real-ban-ronaldo-cho-juventus-172-190891.html\">M.U ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Real b\u00e1n Ronaldo cho Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4126","checkdouble":"190963"},{"date":"11:53 11/07","title":"\u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/7/uy-ban-olympic-chau-a-mac-sai-lam-kho-tin-mon-bong-da-nam-co-the-phai-boc-tham-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) qu\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean hai qu\u1ed1c gia UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i.</h2><h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra. Theo \u0111\u00f3 danh s\u00e1ch 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 tin, K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ed1c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Mac-sai-lam-kho-tin,-Ket-qua-boc-tham-ASIAD-2018-co-the-phai-boc--hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ASIAD 2018 thi\u1ebfu s\u00f3t UAE v\u00e0 Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u1ee6y ban Olympic Qu\u1ed1c gia UAE \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd tham d\u1ef1 \u1edf n\u1ed9i dung n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban Olympic Qu\u1ed1c gia UAE, \u00f4ng Ahmed Al Tayeb \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi UAE kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Palestine.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 100% l\u00e0 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. Kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u sao ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o trong danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m. T\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. \u1ee6y ban Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1, BTC gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n xem x\u00e9t l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng c\u1ea3nh ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi UAE c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0110T Olympic Palestine khi n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y c\u0169ng b\u1ecb BTC &lsquo;b\u1ecf r\u01a1i&rsquo; kh\u1ecfi m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Hi\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 OCA v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng l\u1ea1i hay ph\u00e2n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00e0o 2 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p khi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111ang c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/7/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cac-chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-bang-dau-cua-u23-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-190502.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018, hai chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Asiad 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Jordan v\u1eeba qua ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Asiad 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c danh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4125","checkdouble":"190939"},{"date":"07:14 11/07","title":"\u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real Madrid sang Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 vi\u1ec7c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ph\u00eda Juve \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Ronaldo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1edbi Liverpool, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Los Blancos sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/pele-phat-bieu-ve-ronaldo-va-quyet-dinh-sang-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t c\u1ee5c, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pele c\u1ea3m th\u00f4ng cho Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pele ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 &ldquo;Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1&rdquo; b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u cho h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Pele t\u1eebng tr\u1ea3i qua 18 n\u0103m \u1edf Santos tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o New York Cosmos.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ronaldo-se-da-o-dau-trong-doi-hinh-juventus-180-190857.html\">Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus?</span><br>\r\n<span>Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u00e1t huy h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Xin ch\u00fac m\u1eebng, Cristiano&rdquo;, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. &ldquo;Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Santos song \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Real. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 5 m\u00f9a qua. Trong 9 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e2y l\u00e0m b\u00e0n v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-nham-sao-khung-mu-thay-ronaldo-180-190887.html\">Real nh\u1eafm sao kh\u1ee7ng MU thay Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/david-trezeguet-noi-gi-ve-thuong-vu-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-190885.html\">David Trezeguet n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/emre-can-hao-huc-truoc-co-hoi-choi-bong-cung-ronaldo-184-190838.html\">T\u00e2n binh Juventus h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/buffon-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-juve-chieu-mo-ronaldo-421-190836.html\">Buffon n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Juve chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4124","checkdouble":"190910"}]}